---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const title = "Laundry Room Cabinets: Premium Modular Storage by Klovo";
const description = "Klovo garage cabinets are designed for homeowners who want a premium-looking, well-organized space without hiring a contractor. The moisture-resistant TFL finish and 1mm PVC edge-banding make Klovo equally suited for laundry rooms.";
---

<PageLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="page-hero page-hero--neutral">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
      <span class="eyebrow">Laundry Room</span>
      <h1 class="page-h1">{title}</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
      <article class="prose-klovo">

        <p>Klovo garage cabinets are designed for homeowners who want a premium-looking, well-organized space without hiring a contractor. The moisture-resistant TFL finish and 1mm PVC edge-banding make Klovo equally suited for laundry rooms, where humidity and occasional splashes are common. The GlideLock assembly system allows each cabinet to be assembled in approximately 2–3 minutes — no tools required — making same-day laundry room transformation achievable for any homeowner.</p>

        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions About Laundry Room Cabinets</h2>

        <h3>Are Klovo cabinets suitable for laundry rooms?</h3>
        <p>Yes. Klovo cabinets use a moisture-resistant TFL finish with 1mm PVC edge-banding that protects against the humidity and occasional splashes common in laundry rooms. The clean, furniture-grade aesthetic makes them look right at home next to your washer and dryer.</p>

        <h3>Will laundry room humidity damage Klovo cabinets?</h3>
        <p>No. The TFL (thermally fused laminate) finish is specifically engineered to resist moisture. Unlike raw MDF or particleboard, Klovo's sealed surfaces prevent moisture absorption. For best results, ensure your laundry room has basic ventilation.</p>

        <h3>What can I store in laundry room cabinets?</h3>
        <p>Detergent, fabric softener, dryer sheets, cleaning supplies, iron and ironing board, extra linens and towels, out-of-season clothing, and household cleaning equipment. The 300 lb shelf capacity handles even heavy items like bulk detergent bottles with ease.</p>

        <h3>How do Klovo cabinets fit in a small laundry room?</h3>
        <p>Klovo's modular system starts at just 6 feet wide. You can configure wall-mounted upper cabinets above your washer/dryer to maximize vertical space without sacrificing floor area.</p>

        <h3>Do I need a contractor to install laundry room cabinets?</h3>
        <p>No. Klovo's GlideLock system assembles each cabinet in about 2–3 minutes with no tools required. Wall mounting does require a drill for the wall anchors, but the cabinets themselves need zero tools to assemble.</p>

        <h3>How do Klovo laundry room cabinets compare to custom built-ins?</h3>
        <p>Custom laundry room cabinetry typically costs $3,000–$8,000 and requires a contractor. Klovo's modular system delivers a premium look and finish at a fraction of the cost with same-day DIY installation.</p>

        <h2>Related Resources</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/pages/garage-cabinets">Garage Cabinet Systems &rarr;</a></li>
          <li><a href="/pages/entryway-cabinets">Entryway &amp; Mudroom Cabinets &rarr;</a></li>
          <li><a href="/pages/garage-organization-systems">Garage Organization Systems &rarr;</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blogs/news/why-kitchen-grade-cabinets-belong-in-your-garage">Why Kitchen-Grade Cabinets Belong in Your Garage &rarr;</a></li>
        </ul>

      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style is:global>
.prose-klovo { font-family: var(--sans); color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.75; }
.prose-klovo h2 { font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(22px,2.8vw,30px); color: var(--ink); margin: 48px 0 16px; }
.prose-klovo h3 { font-family: var(--display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 20px; color: var(--ink); margin: 36px 0 12px; }
.prose-klovo p { margin: 0 0 20px; }
.prose-klovo ul, .prose-klovo ol { padding-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.prose-klovo li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
.prose-klovo strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
.prose-klovo a { color: var(--amber); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }
.prose-klovo a:hover { color: var(--ink); }
</style>
